        "subject": "LU-1206 mdt: Call mdt_write_allow on mo_open error",
        "message": "LU-1206 mdt: Call mdt_write_allow on mo_open error\n\nIn the case that mdt_mfd_open is called with the MDS_FMODE_EXEC flag\nset, but mo_open returns an error, the mdt_write_deny call is not\nproperly balanced with a mdt_write_allow call. This patch adds the\nneeded invocation of mdt_write_allow.\n\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I99d5d4b2dcb775a691525f7077f33df31b214861\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
